            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/jake/level1/jakeOnBreakEvening-3.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Jake pockets a handful of coins from a nearby table.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress3">>Three bucks. Not terrible for an evening tip. Could buy half a burger.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Don't spend it all at once.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress3">>I'm investing it. In vending machine snacks. Have a good break out here.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Thanks.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress3">>No problem.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 2, trust: 1
